Review_Summary: The stones, steel vessel and plastic are of fine quality. Easy to operate. Motor is super powerful at the first use. I will re-review after some more use. As the main operation is doing by the motor and stones, we have to compromise on the sound generated while operating. Packing was good and the product got delivered surprisingly faster. 3 days before the promised date.
